name: land-use-and-land-cover-cemeteries-usgs-bla-in-cemetery-locations-in-indiana-united-states-geo
notes: Cemeteries_USGSs__BLA_IN is a point shapefile showing the locations and attribute values of cemeteries extracted from the Geographic Names Information System (GNIS) developed by the USGS. The dataset contains cemeteries named on USGS 1:24000 quadrangles and other source map data. Some portions of the southwestern counties were field checked. Unnamed cemeteries were added from 1:24000 quadrangles (see process step) by Bernardin, Lochmueller and Associates.
